    section
      h2 The Problem

      p In early 2022, my Technical Lead and I were tasked with finding a way to drive more users to the Observability platform during onboarding. I lead the project alongside an Engineering Technical Lead. We worked across the Observability organization as well as with the Elastic UI design system team to establish cohesion throughout the product. The following case study shows the end to end product design effort which resulted in a Saved Views feature being implemented in the Observability Logs solution.

    section
      h2 Impact

      ul
        li Frustrating Developer experience due to the lack of a Design System or guidelines.
        li Bottlenecks between design + engineering make it hard to move quickly and iterate.
        li Inconsistent UI doesn't inspire a sense of safety and trust for users.
        li Competitors products are more polished and they are beating us even though our feature offering is more complete.

