      h2 General Audience Release 

      p For GA, we updated chunks of the product at the time based on components and used feature flags to test with certain segments of users. Six weeks before GA, we flipped on the new styles for our internal organization. This allowed us to continue to test and gather feedback leading up to release.

      p Our GTM team helped us recruit customers who were willing to test out the new UI. This allowed us to release small chunks at a time and get feedback in real time. We conducted live and async sessions and gathered feedback in a shared Slack channel.

